- **docs/DECISIONS.md** – Architecture and development decisions. Follow existing decisions; record new ones here.
- **docs/FEATURES.md** – Implemented and planned features. Update when adding, removing, or changing a feature.
- **docs/NOTATION.md** – Naming, file layout, and conventions. Follow these when adding or editing code.
- **docs/UI_DESIGN.md** – UI tokens, layouts, and components. Follow and update when changing the UI.
